 TIKTOK SENSATION Nova Ellisson has shot to fame thanks to the fact she's the spitting image of arguably one of the most famous women in the world - Kylie Jenner. Nova's TikToks have racked up millions of views, prompting a wave of support as well as some backlash, with some users telling her to "be herself". Nova, who has a young daughter, hasn't shied away from addressing the hate as she has come out and responded to several comments while defending her moment in the spotlight. With her rising popularity, now Nova is leaning into the Kylie look to promote her upcoming skincare company. Today, she is heading into town to get a Kylie makeover from her friend, a makeup artist working for Kylie Cosmetics.
